Name: Phantom: Thundering Mephis
UndiscoveredDes: An Overlord Class Whisperin TD found in Desorock Highland. It demonstrates combat abilities similar to those of a human.
DiscoveredDes:
This enemy has a higher RES to Electro DMG.

A powerful TD based in Desorock Highland with the power of thunder. It is considered one of the vanguards in the Threnodian's army.
